            and is Copyright 2012 by the Concord Consortium, All Rights are Reserved.
          %p
            However this Interactive and all of the code to create it are available in
            Concord Consortium's
            %a{:href => "https://github.com/concord-consortium/lab"} Lab
            software repository and distributed to you under multiple open-source licenses.
          %p
            Concord Consortium's
            %a{:href => "https://github.com/concord-consortium/lab"}  Lab
            software and content are Copyright 2012 (c) by the Concord Consortium and are
            distributed under any of the following licenses:
            %a{:href => "http://www.opensource.org/licenses/BSD-2-Clause"} Simplified BSD
            ,
            %a{:href => "http://www.opensource.org/licenses/MIT"} MIT
            , and
            %a{:href => "http://www.opensource.org/licenses/Apache-2.0"} Apache 2.0

    %script{:src => "../../lab/lab.js", :type => "text/javascript"}
    %script{:src => "../../imports/legacy-mw-content/model-list.js", :type => "text/javascript"}
    %script{:src => "application.js", :type => "text/javascript"}

